### Cacat #9: Cronjob Produk Unggulan Hardcoded

> [!NOTE]
> **File:** [Dokumentasi Microservice ARIMA.md](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/flask/Dokumentasi%20Microservice%20ARIMA%20%26%20Pipeline.md) ‚Äî Baris 242

**Masalah:** Daftar produk untuk cronjob ARIMA **di-hardcode** di `routes/console.php`:
```php
$topProducts = ['Tunik molek', 'rok plisket', 'gamis set outer alzea'];
```
Jika admin menambah/menghapus produk, cronjob tidak otomatis menyesuaikan.

**Solusi:** Tarik produk unggulan secara dinamis dari database, misalnya top 5 produk dengan order terbanyak dalam 30 hari terakhir:
```php
$topProducts = OrderItem::select('products.name')
    ->join('products', 'order_items.product_id', '=', 'products.id')
    ->join('orders', 'order_items.order_id', '=', 'orders.id')
    ->where('orders.status', 'completed')
    ->where('orders.created_at', '>=', now()->subDays(30))
    ->groupBy('products.name')
    ->orderByRaw('SUM(order_items.qty) DESC')
    ->limit(5)
    ->pluck('products.name');
```

